<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.3">
<l>kañcaik kāynta karuvilli kaṭaikka ṇeṉṉuñ ciṟaikkōlāl</l>
<l>neñcū ṭuruva vēvuṇṭu nilaiyun taḷarntu naivēṉai</l>
<l>añcē leṉṉā ṉavaṉoruva ṉavaṉmār vaṇinta vaṉamālai</l>
<l>vañci yātē tarumākil mārviṟ koṇarntu puraṭṭīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If that one Man—who does not say, ‘Do not fear!’ to me who have grown faint</l>
<l>Having been burned as the [Lord with] black bow[-like eyebrows] who burned Kaṃsa</l>
<l>Pierced through [my] heart by means of the winged arrow that is [His] sideglance—</l>
<l>Gives without cheating the tulsi garland that He wore on [His] chest,</l>
<l rend="indent">	Bring [that] and rub [it] against [my] chest, [o friends]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
